a_n = 3^n - 2^{n+100}(n \in \mathbb{N})
a_n = 3^n (1- 2^{100} \cdot \left(\frac{2}{3}\right)^n)
 a_n=3^n\left( 1- 2^{100}\left(\frac{2}{3}\right)^n\right). 
a_n=3^n-2^{n+100}=3^n-2^{100}\times 2^n=2^n((\frac{3}{2})^n-2^{100})\to +\infty
n\to +\infty
